Welcome to
                	                		Command Security Corporation            		
CSC and Aviation Safeguards are dedicated to serving our customers and our nation by enabling the safe conduct of commerce and public life. CSC is not foreign owned, and is the only publicly traded (NYSE-MOC) U.S. owned and operated security company in the industry. CSC is not distracted by mergers, acquisitions, or industry consolidation integration; and is always interested in bringing on talented and committed employees. If you have been downsized or affected by industry consolidation activity, we would love to hear from you. Please contact us or visit our Career area.
Request a Quote | Learn More About CSC 




 








Full-Service
Our custom plans and specialized training academy provide each employee with the knowledge and skill to handle any security need.

View Our Services 

 






Training
We have a 12-step screening process and a long-standing proven track record for more than 6,500 highly trained security professionals.

View Our Training Process 

 






Experience
Our executive team brings high-level expertise from the homeland security and the defense marketplace.

View Our Team 

 






About Our Company
Command Security Corporation (CSC) is a team of professionals focused on providing full-solution security services. We provide high-quality, dependable protection services that are adaptable to meet the constantly changing security challenges and fluctuating market conditions. 





