Command Security Corp Employee Statistics




School/University


Top Degrees


Also Worked at


Time at Command Security Corp

























                                                Candidates seeking jobs at Command Security Corp hail from universities all over the country, but certain institutions stand out above the rest. Berkshire Community College alumni represent 5.26%, G.E.D - Quinsigamond Community College accounts for 2.63% of candidates, and Newell Secondary School makes up 2.63%.
                                            

                                                Trends in employee education at Command Security Corp reveal a lot about the company's intellectual environment.  Overall, the most common educational background among employees at Command Security Corp is high school graduate (30.56% of workers). Following are GED holders (8.33% of workers).
                                            

                                                Applicants seeking opportunities at Command Security Corp have also shown interest in US Security Associates, Security - Security Operations & Solutions, Time Cap Labs Inc, Hess Express, and Pinkerton Government Services.
                                            



























