Command Security Corp reports Q4 loss per share $0.14
Monday, 27 Jun 2016 07:00am EDT 
Command Security Corp  : Says "well positioned for strong revenue growth and increased operating income in fiscal year 2017" . Command Security Corporation reports financial results for three months and fiscal year ended March 31, 2016 . Quarterly loss per share $0.14 .Quarterly revenue $31.4 million versus $32.7 million. 
			
