            Command Security Corporation is one of the leading providers of security services in the United States. The company has a staff of more than 4,500 trained and certified security professionals. It offers services to various the government, education, health care and retail industries. Command Security Corporation also operates several subsidiaries, including Rodgers Police Patrol and Strategic Security Services. The company conducts security training sessions for employees that include specialized instruction by certified trainers and fire safety, crowd and riot control, media interaction, public relations, crisis and emergency situation handling techniques. It additionally serves real estate, construction and multitenant facilities. Command Security Corporation maintains a location in New York City.
          






















